<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Event Creation Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #8e44ad;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Event Creation Confirmation</h2>
    <p>Hello <%= organizerName %>,</p>
    <p>Your event "<%= eventName %>" has been successfully created.</p>
    <p>Event Details:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Event Name:</strong> <%= eventName %></li>
      <li><strong>Start Date:</strong> <%= eventStartDate %></li>
      <li><strong>End Date:</strong> <%= eventEndDate %></li>
      <li><strong>Location:</strong> <%= location %></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Thank you for organizing with us!</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>Agenda Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
